Three gymnasts from Zanis Gymnastics Academy proved to be the best in their respective age groups during the South African Gymnastics Federation (SAGF) Zanis Level 2 Age Group competition held at Zanis recently. Nearly 200 gymnasts competed in the tournament. Zani s members Reatlegile Ledwaba, girls u.8, Phindulo Mainganye, u.11 and Tara Thompson, u.7 won their respective categories to walk away with the gold. Story and photo: ENDY SENYATSI &gt;&gt;endy@observer.co.za &nbsp;